extends layout

block content
	div#content
		div#books.column.column_pad
			h1 Available Now
			div.cushion_right.cushion_bottom
				a(href="/the_alderman")
					img.book_cover.cushion_right(src="/images/alderman_cover_icon.jpg", height="114", width="80")
				a(href="/the_alderman")
					h2 The Alderman
				p Seven noble sons promised riches in exchange for completing a suicide mission. 
				div.clear
			div.cushion_right
				h1 Recent Posts
				div#recent_entries
		div#current_news.column
			h1 Current News ...
			h2 12.24.13
			p The River Goddess backstory was so much fun that I think I'll write about that as a short work after I finish this book about the Tempest and the Selters.
			h2 12.17.13
			p Well, my intention to write a quaint novella has gone awry.  It's turning into a novel.  The map below is the part of the Waning where it takes place.
			div.clear
				a(class="fancybox", rel="group", href="images/selter-valley.png")
					img.book_cover(src="images/t_selter-valley.png", width="386", height="145", alt="Selter Valley")
			h2 12.8.13
			p I started dabbling with a short story about the Tempest getting a cup of coffee.  It's set just before the Dead Wars, during a stretch when he was disengaged from much of the world.
		div.clear

	link(rel="stylesheet", href="/js/fancybox/source/jquery.fancybox.css?v=2.1.3", type="text/css", media="screen")
	script(type="text/javascript", src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.8.3/jquery.min.js")
	script(type="text/javascript", src="/js/fancybox/source/jquery.fancybox.pack.js?v=2.1.3")
	script.
		$(function() { 
			$(".fancybox").fancybox();
			$.getJSON('http://blog.endleland.com/api/read/json?callback=?',
						function(response) {
							var i=0;
							var d="";
							var p = "";
							for (post in response.posts) {
								if(i<3) {
									d = new Date(response.posts[post]['date-gmt']);
									p += '<div><a href="' + response.posts[post].url+ '">' + (d.getMonth()+1) + "/" + d.getFullYear() + " - " + response.posts[post]['regular-title'] + "</div>";
									i++;
								}
								else
									break;
							}
							$("#recent_entries").html(p);	
					});
		});
		
		
			